data.description: FRESHLY PAINTED SOUTH HILLS HOME! Every surface has been touched to get this 3 bedroom 3 bath home ready for the market! The finished basement includes a full bath and could easily be used for a guest suite. Close to Marilla Park and Pool, Rail Trail, and sandwiched conveniently between Sabraton/I-68 and downtown, don't miss the opportunity to tour this home and see first hand it's convenient location & panoramic views!
